N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4214.3 - Rulings after official declaration

State Regulations

Rulings of the judges with regard to the award of purse
money made after the result has been declared official shall in no way affect
the mutuel payoff. Notes
